hcc_text: Utopia Parkway is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top third for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in Queens)
info: At Utopia Parkway at 186th Street, 48th Avenue and Gladwin Avenue, there was 1 severe injury in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
